Package: quakeR
Type: Package
Title: Package for working with the NOAA Significant Earthquakes dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Vadim Bondarenko
Maintainer: Vadim Bondarenko <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: The NOAA Significant Earthquakes dataset has a substantial amount 
  of information that is not immediately accessible to people without knowledge 
  of the intimate details of the dataset or of R. 
  This package provides the tools for processing and visualizing the data so that 
  others may extract some use out of the information embedded within.
